# Repo cache for codebase rehydration (clone-once-then-fetch)
.cache/

# Per-eval JSON result files (pass-rate reports)
**/results/

# Eval cases carry client data and live in a separate PRIVATE repo, located via
# DIFFS_EVAL_CASES_DIR (see README.md). They must NEVER be committed here; this
# is a safety net against an accidental local checkout or capture under the
# in-tree default path being re-added.
**/cases/
